Token.Abstract: @brief Initializes a newly allocated dictionary with the contents of data. Data must be property list.

Parameter.Name: data
Parameter.Abstract: An NSData object containing bytes of plist file representation.

ReturnValue.Abstract: A dictionary initialized to contain the contents in data. Returns nil if the contents of the request can’t be parsed into a dictionary. The returned object might be different than the original receiver.
